    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. i'm hearing a lot of concern from local shop owners that these costs are basically going to force them to close or move overseas. do you think these regulations are actually sustainable for the small business sector, or are they more of an ideological push that ignores the practical economic reality?",
